                    <T n="single">0x2420F304<!--A poster with a small piece of paper taped to the edge is hung under a sign for Tomarani Tributes. {0.SimFirstName} unfolds this mystery note to read:\n\n<i>Generations long ago, the sleepy fishing village of Tomarang sat just off the coast of the Shih Sea. Tigers were known to walk the tree line, protecting the village from any danger that lurked within the surrounding forests. Villagers honored their guardians by offering food from their abundant riverways.\n\nBut as time went on, the small village grew in size and their leader began to redistribute resources away from the tigers. Without any provisions at the forest's edge, the tiger pack withdrew to seek sustenance elsewhere. It wasn't long before the village faced the dire consequences of this loss, as beasts began to descend upon them.</i>\n\nHm. The note ends there, but the story feels unfinished. How strange.--></T>
